    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-11-30T08:35:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-11-30T08:35:00-05:00" n="297"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d297">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.20/177: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tehran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-11-30T17:00:00+03:25"
                            >November 30, 1942—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received November 30—3:39 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>410. My 357, November 2 and Department’s instruction No. 155, November 5.
                    Schwarzkopf requests that the signing of agreement with Iran covering his
                    mission be expedited since he feels it will be difficult to establish his
                    organization and authority until his status is clearly defined.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
